{"EPIMACHUS":[{"def":"A genus of highly ornate and brilliantly colored birds of Australia, allied to the birds of Paradise.","pos":""}],"EPIMERAL":[{"def":"Pertaining to the epimera.","pos":""}],"EPIMERE":[{"def":"One of the segments of the transverse axis, or the so called homonymous parts; as, for example, one of the several segments of the extremities in vertebrates, or one of the similar segments in plants, such as the segments of a segmented leaf.","pos":""}]}